headline: Beni Unveils Beni Lens: The First Visual Search Engine for Secondhand Fashion - Making Thrifting as Easy as Shopping New
summary: Today, Beni, the AI-powered resale search engine, announced the launch of Beni Lens, a breakthrough visual search technology that allows shoppers to instantly find secondhand versions of anything that inspires them — online or in real life.
